README for installing Unity on Ubuntu (xubuntu 14.04)

This was in /usr/local/src/Unity/

See release news at URL:
http://forum.unity3d.com/threads/unity-on-linux-release-notes-and-known-issues.350256/

# Found this URL on that page:
wget http://download.unity3d.com/download_unity/linux/unity-editor-5.4.0b18+20160524_amd64.deb

#As root:
gdebi unity-editor-5.4.0b18+20160524_amd64.deb


# run not as root (in /usr/local/src/Unity)
./post_install.bash

